# Sunburst - KX Dashboards

Original URL: https://code.kx.com/dashboards/sunburst/

# Sunburst Chart

![Screenshot](../img/sunburst/sunburst.jpg)

An inner circle surrounded by rings of deeper hierarchy levels. The angle of
each segment is proportional to a value or divided equally under its parent
node.

## Set up

  1. Assign a data source.

  2. Set _Breakdown_ with a [view state parameter](../viewstateparameters/) of type `list`, with the categories from your data source.

## _Basics_

![Screenshot](../img/sunburst/sunburstbasics.png)

_Name_

    A name for the component provided by the user. 
_Data Source_

     [Data sources](../datasources/)
_Focus_

    A [view state parameter](../viewstateparameters/) for [linking](../viewstateparameters/#linking-components) components
_Node Click_

    Select between `default`, a fixed sunburst chart displaying all hierarchies as a single entity at all times, or `rootToNode` which redraws the chart based on the selected hierarchial interaction. 
_Selected Value_

_Selected Value Attribute_

    A [view state parameter](../viewstateparameters/) storing the selected hierarchy level as defined by _Selected Value Attribute_. _Selected Value Attribute_ is one of `name`, `value` or `dataIndex`

## Data

![Screenshot](../img/sunburst/sunburstdata.jpg)

_Breakdown_

    Type `list` [view state parameter](../viewstateparameters/) to define hierarchial levels from the [data source](../datasources/).
_Weight_

    Dependent (numeric) variable from [data source](../datasources/) to define node size. 

_Color_

option | description  
---|---  
`default` | Shared color across node hierarchies  
`fixed` | One color across all nodes  
`level` | Different colors at each hierarchial level  
`visual map` | Gradient color by _Weight_ range,  
Data column | Selected from the [data source](../datasources/).  
  
## Config

![Screenshot](../img/sunburst/sunburstconfig.jpg)

_Radius Inner_

_Radius Outer_

    A _Radius Inner_ value above zero adds a 'doughnut' hole to the Sunburst chart. A _Radius Outer_ value at 100 bounds the sunburst chart to the top and bottom of the component boundaries. 

### Label

_Show_

_Display_

    Toggle to show _Display_ labels for each node value; _Display_ values taken from a column in the [data source](../datasources/).
_Color_

    Font color for labels
_Rotate_

_Position_

_Align_

    Set position and alignment of labels.

#### Font

_Radius Outer_

_Radius Inner_

    Font size and font style of node labels. 

#### Format

_Format_

    Format of label 
_Decimal_

_Hide Trailing Zeroes_

    For numeric _Formats_
_Date/Time Format_

    For Datetime _Format_
_Prefix_

_Suffix_

    Add a piece of text, e.g. currency symbol or percentage, before or after the label.
_Threshold_

    Frequency of node labels. 
_Fit Text_

    Select between `Shorten Text` or `Overflow` for the fit of labels.

### Visual map

Configuration for visual map of data color options

_Type_

    Select between `continuous` gradient or defined `piecewise`
_Label Color_

    Font color of _Pieces_ label
_Min_

_Max_

    Range of visual-map gradient
_Pieces_

    Number of `piecewise` sections to use for visual map

Display rollover of node values and labels

